snippet.title: Warcraft: Orcs & Humans - Introduction
snippet.description:
The good old Warcraft introduction, the game which began it all :)
(the Warcraft mayhem, not the realtime strategy genre of course).
Wikipedia: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Warcraft:_Orcs_and_Humans
